Line Chart 6
  1. Click under Visualizations panel on line chart
  2. Click and drag Date Field onto the Axis for line chart where it says "Add data fields here"
  3. Click and drag .CA Confirmed into the Values Field where it says "Add data fields here"
  4. Repeat same steps for .CA Confirmed with .CA Death / .CA Recovered / .CA Existing (in that order)
  1. Rename Values as Confirmed / Deaths / Recovered / Existing by double clicking on .CA... tiles 

Then click on the Paintbrush (Format) icon under the visualizations pane and configure as seen below
